      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.9999999881
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが祇園ですわね！\n噂通り、美味しそうなものが沢山ありますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this is Gion!\nJust as rumored‚ there are so many delicious-looking things!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "フルーツ飴に、お団子……どれも選べませんわ！\n{user}さんはどれがいいと思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fruit candy‚ dango… I can't choose one!\nWhat do you think would be good‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5995203853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……せっかくだし\nすずが食べたいものを食べたらいいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… since we're here‚\nI think you should eat what you want to eat‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3000001271,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9369.999872900004,
          "startTime": 29.67
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、私あのお団子にしますわ！\n{user}さん、待っててくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll have that dango!\nPlease wait for me‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9000006358,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5391.880289700001,
          "startTime": 32.2918809255
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.8918809255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "お団子、買ってきましたわ……\nおばさんが一本おまけをくださいましたの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have bought some dango…\nThe lady gave me an extra one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、良かったじゃないか\nじゃあ、なんでそんなに落ち込んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's good.\nThen why are you so down?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6260785302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ぐぬぬぬ……\n屈辱ですわ～……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Arrrgh…\nIt's humiliating~…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2652859887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "「お嬢ちゃん、お兄ちゃんとお買い物？　一人で頼めて\n偉いね～！　お団子、一本おまけしとくわ！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Little girl‚ shopping with your big brother? You can order by yourself\nso well~! I'll give you an extra dango!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2838277381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "……って言われましたの！　私もう十五歳ですのに……\nそんなに子供っぽくないですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's what she said! I'm fifteen already…\nI'm not that childish!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1400151771
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……\nそれは判断が難し……いや、許せないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nThat's hard to judge… I mean‚ that's unforgivable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5883589944
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "今、判断が難しい、と言いかけませんでした！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn't you just start to say \"hard to judge\"!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5883589944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5828229786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや……そんな訳ないだろう\nあ！　あんな所に舞妓さんがいるぞ、すず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no… that can't be right.\nOh! There's an apprentice geisha over there‚ Suzu!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "話を逸らそうとしても無駄ですのよ！\nそんな手に乗る成宮すずでは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's useless trying to change the subject!\nSuzu Narumiya won't fall for such tricks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.2811513464
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "あら……確かに綺麗ですわね\n紅葉の模様の着物がとても映えていますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my… she's certainly beautiful.\nThe kimono with autumn leaf patterns looks so wonderful on her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8333409627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "大人っぽくて……なんて優雅なんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's so mature… how elegant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.712026139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.37148422
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "美しい着物に高い下駄で歩く姿が綺麗だな\nきっとすずと同じくらいの年じゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way she walks in that beautiful kimono and high geta is lovely.\nI bet she's around the same age as you‚ Suzu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3666742961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.310331126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.310331126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。舞妓さんは、中学卒業後、寮に入って\n厳しい修業を経てプロの芸妓さんになれるらしいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Apprentice geishas move into dormitories after middle school\nand undergo strict training to become professional geishas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1000111898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3170153577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなのためにガイド本を読み漁った）\n（知識が活きたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The knowledge I had gained from guidebooks for everyone）\n（came in handy.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2333445232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですの……！\nなんだか星見プロのアイドルと似てますのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…!\nIt's somehow similar to the idols at Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3000142416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4778738776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "私と近い年であんなに大人びて艶っぽいだなんて……\n憧れてしまいますわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being so mature and alluring at an age close to mine…\nI can't help but admire her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.633347575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.344171504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "私、もっと舞妓さんについて知りたいです！\n{user}さん、案内してくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to know more about apprentice geishas!\nPlease guide me‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8000203451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.80723627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、調べてみるよ……\nお、この近くで舞妓さんが踊るイベントがあるみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright‚ I'll look it up…\nOh‚ there seems to be an event where apprentice geishas dance nearby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.833355713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
